  "body": "The data you read from or write to a file are lists of bytes, which appear in Pd as lists of numbers from 0 to 255 (using out-of-range numbers of symbols leads to undefined behaviour.) The 2nd inlet of the 'file handle' object is documented in the 'file define' subpatch."
